org.tmatesoft.svn.core.wc
Class SVNDiffStatus

java.lang.Object
  org.tmatesoft.svn.core.wc.SVNDiffStatus
public class SVNDiffStatus
extends Object

The SVNDiffStatus class is used to provide short information on path changes during diff status operations.

Since:
1.1.0
Version:
1.2.0

TMate Software Ltd.
